LinkedIn Scheduled Post Editor

Fixing a typo in a scheduled Linkedin Post means deleting it and then you have to copy paste again. Not anymore. Introducing a quick, free and user-friendly way to edit your scheduled posts.

How it works?
This extension adds a custom edit button to your scheduled posts, allowing you to edit your scheduled post right away.

- No need to leave LinkedIn
- Simple to use
- 100% free
